0.2.0b 2/10
------

- general changes:
	Fully reworking the module towards a new storage scheme.

- class Characteristic:
	__init__(shape)
	append(dependency)
	get_dispersion()
	__iadd__(other)
	__mul__(other)
	__rmul__(other)
	__getitem__((shape, key))
	__setitem__(key, value)
	__len__()
	flatten(new_shape, *, **)
	repeat(new_shape, *, **)
	reshape(new_shape, *, **)
	broadcast(shape)
	broadcasted(shape)

